# Puchi Infrastructure

Infrastructure as Code — ArgoCD GitOps trên K3s 3-node HA.

## Cluster

| Node | IP | Role |
|------|-----|------|
| k3s-node1 | 192.168.100.201 | control-plane, etcd |
| k3s-node2 | 192.168.100.202 | control-plane, etcd |
| k3s-node3 | 192.168.100.203 | control-plane, etcd |

K3s v1.35.5, storage: `local-path`, ingress: Traefik.

## Cấu trúc repo

```
puchi-infra/
├── argocd/
│   ├── projects/infra.yaml     # AppProject: puchi
│   └── apps/
│       ├── root.yaml            # App of Apps root
│       ├── repo-creds.yaml      # GitHub token
│       ├── puchi-db.yaml        # PostgreSQL clusters
│       ├── supertokens.yaml     # Supertoken auth
│       └── envoy-gateway.yaml   # Envoy Gateway
├── infra/
│   └── postgres-cluster/       # CloudNativePG CRDs
├── scripts/
│   ├── bootstrap.sh            # ArgoCD bootstrap
│   ├── setup-garage.sh         # Garage buckets
│   └── setup-nats.sh           # NATS streams
└── README.md
```

## Services dùng chung với Arda

| Service | Namespace | Mô tả |
|---------|-----------|-------|
| CloudNativePG | cnpg-system | PostgreSQL operator |
| NATS | platform | Message broker, prefix `puchi.*` |
| Garage | platform | S3 storage, bucket `puchi-*` |
| Valkey (Redis) | platform | Cache, DB index riêng |
| Traefik | kube-system | Ingress controller |
| ArgoCD | argocd | GitOps deploy |
| Cloudflare Tunnel | platform | Expose ra internet |

## Services riêng của Puchi

| Service | Chart | Namespace |
|---------|-------|-----------|
| PostgreSQL | CloudNativePG CRD | puchi-db |
| Supertoken | supertokens/helm | puchi-infra |
| Envoy Gateway | envoy/gateway-helm | envoy-gateway-system |
